nodes.text: Fezmix was a Bonbrak male who worked with the Jedi Padawan Ram Jomaram in his garage in Lonisa City during the High Republic Era. Jomaram considered him to be rowdy.
Fezmix first appeared in the novel The High Republic: Race to Crashpoint Tower. The character was named "Femix" in a preview of the book published in The High Republic: A Test of Courage.
